/171581400/image_171581400.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/171581400/image_171581400.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">AZemdega</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Overview</h2> <p>With the markets recently selling off after the Fed's latest 25 basis point <a href=\"https://cnbc.com/2024/12/18/fed-cuts-interest-rates-by-25-basis-points-what-will-get-cheaper.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">rate cut</a>, some investors are panicked. However, I'd advise us all to take this as an opportunity to really see the discounted valuations we've been give</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/171581400/image_171581400.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745767-realty-income-dont-over-think-this-christmas-discount-on-reliable-income", "pub_date": "2024-12-21 13:24:04", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4745763", "title": "Abbott Laboratories: A Future-Driven Pharma Brand With A Robust Pipeline", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2024514092/image_2024514092.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Vaccine Production Facility. Medication Manufacturing Process. Glass Vials with Orange Caps on Conveyor Belt. Medical Ampoule Production Line at Modern Pharmaceutical Factory.\" data-id=\"2024514092\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"864px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2024514092/image_2024514092.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2024514092/image_2024514092.jpg?io=ge